<p>I‚Äôm about to start as Director of Engineering for <a href="https://www.strataoncology.com/" target="_blank">Strata Oncology</a>. Ahead of my start I‚Äôve been reflecting on what successes I may repeat and what failures I may avoid from my time at <a href="https://duo.com/" target="_blank">Duo Security</a> after 5+ years.</p>

